author: olegk
msg: Use RFC 2109 cookie spec as a fallback cookie policy when dealing with older cookies.

It is not a very good idea to look up the fallback spec by id using CookiePolicy.getCookieSpec, as (at least in theory) one can register any arbitrary cookie policy for that id, whereas we definitely want specific behaviour from a specific cookie spec
